2026-06-23 21:27:29,890 DEBUG msg #34: UserMessage tool_result(toolu_01XyKAfuSdNqPEpLiNtDjVUJ): 1	"""Bracket builder: generates a World Cup knockout bracket TOML from live standings/teams."""
