# Prompt — Phase 3-4: Implementing a GitHub Issue (TDD)

**Model:** `claude-sonnet-4-6`
**Tools:** `Agent`, `Read`, `Edit`, `Write`, `Bash`, `Glob`, `Grep`, `WebSearch`, `WebFetch`, `context7` (MCP)

